title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should display in data set dialog.
OB: On the query result page, the output parameter is not displayed in the edit data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be displayed in the edit data set dialog.
SR:
To reproduce the issue:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the query result in the edit data set dialog and verify if the output parameter is being displayed.
